import_cosmed
=============

Description
-----------

This function imports a COSMED indirect calorimetry data file

Usage
-----

.. code:: r

   import_cosmed(file, file_out)

Arguments
---------

-  ``file``: input file
-  ``file_out``: output file

Examples
--------

.. code:: r

   import_cosmed(input_file, output_file)
